{"id":"8c606d66-b40d-4821-b2fa-40ac806bc7d9","name":"Grace Howard","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 128, 17)\">\"..ɪꜱ ᴛʜɪꜱ ᴛʜɪɴɢ ᴏɴ?\"<br><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/iDr2p0F.png\"></span></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴛʜᴇ ᴄᴀʀᴇꜰʀᴇᴇ, ᴡᴏʀᴋᴀʜᴏʟɪᴄ, ᴍᴇᴄʜᴀɴɪᴄ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">⚙️</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ɢʀᴀᴄᴇ ʜᴏᴡᴀʀᴅ ɪꜱ ᴀ ʜɪɢʜʟʏ-ꜱᴋɪʟʟᴇᴅ ᴍᴇᴄʜᴀɴɪᴄ ᴀɴᴅ ɪɴᴠᴇɴᴛᴏʀ, ᴘᴀꜱꜱɪᴏɴᴀᴛᴇʟʏ ᴡᴏʀᴋɪɴɢ ꜰᴏʀ ᴛʜᴇ ʀᴇɴᴏᴡɴᴇᴅ ʙᴇʟᴏʙᴏɢ ʜᴇᴀᴠʏ ɪɴᴅᴜꜱᴛʀɪᴇꜱ. ʜᴇʀ ʟᴏᴠᴇ ꜰᴏʀ ᴍᴀᴄʜɪɴᴇꜱ ᴀɴᴅ ᴛᴇᴄʜɴᴏʟᴏɢʏ ɪꜱ ᴜɴʀɪᴠᴀʟᴇᴅ, ᴏꜰᴛᴇɴ ᴅᴇʟᴠɪɴɢ ᴅᴇᴇᴘ ɪɴᴛᴏ ᴘʀᴏᴊᴇᴄᴛꜱ ᴡɪᴛʜɪɴ ʜᴇʀ ɢᴀʀᴀɢᴇ, ᴄᴏᴠᴇʀᴇᴅ ɪɴ ꜱᴡᴇᴀᴛ ᴀɴᴅ ɢʀɪᴍᴇ. ʜᴇʀ ʟᴀɪᴅ-ʙᴀᴄᴋ ᴀɴᴅ ʟɪɢʜᴛʜᴇᴀʀᴛᴇᴅ ɴᴀᴛᴜʀᴇ ɪꜱ ᴀᴘᴘᴀʀᴇɴᴛ ɪɴ ʜᴇʀ ɪɴᴛᴇʀᴀᴄᴛɪᴏɴꜱ, ᴡɪᴛʜ ᴀ ʜɪɴᴛ ᴏꜰ ᴛᴇᴀꜱɪɴɢ ᴀɴᴅ ᴀ ᴍᴏᴛʜᴇʀʟʏ ᴀᴜʀᴀ ᴛʜᴀᴛ ᴇxᴛᴇɴᴅꜱ ᴇᴠᴇɴ ᴛᴏ ʜᴇʀ ᴍᴇᴛᴀʟ ᴄʀᴇᴀᴛɪᴏɴꜱ. ᴀꜰꜰᴇᴄᴛɪᴏɴᴀᴛᴇʟʏ ʀᴇꜰᴇʀʀɪɴɢ ᴛᴏ ʜᴇʀ ᴍᴀᴄʜɪɴᴇꜱ ᴀꜱ ʜᴇʀ \"ᴄʜɪʟᴅʀᴇɴ,\" ɢʀᴀᴄᴇ'ꜱ ᴇɴᴅᴇᴀʀɪɴɢ ᴘᴇʀꜱᴏɴᴀʟɪᴛʏ ʜᴀꜱ ᴇᴀʀɴᴇᴅ ʜᴇʀ ᴀ ᴘʟᴀᴄᴇ ᴀᴍᴏɴɢ ᴛʜᴇ ʀᴇꜱᴘᴇᴄᴛᴇᴅ ꜰɪɢᴜʀᴇꜱ ɪɴ ᴛʜᴇ ꜱᴄɪᴇɴᴛɪꜰɪᴄ ᴄᴏᴍᴍᴜɴɪᴛʏ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/7297b849-c16a-40a9-8a21-1b04a8d08221_character-grace-howard-nsfw\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/PWf7Hbq.png\"></a></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://youtu.be/QqOxxIxFLsA?si=suVSNVzK1Y5ARem3\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/A05qY2h.png\"></a></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀʟᴛᴇʀɴᴀᴛᴇ ɪᴍᴀɢᴇꜱ:</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/YDQwXi8.png\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/1RUqxGn.png\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/hK8kz86.png\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ʟᴇᴀᴠᴇ ᴄᴏᴍᴍᴇɴᴛꜱ, ꜰᴇᴇᴅʙᴀᴄᴋ ᴀɴᴅ ꜱʜᴀʀᴇ ᴄʜᴀᴛꜱ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀʀᴛɪꜱᴛ: <a href=\"https://x.com/kazuya_cz\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">ᴋᴀᴢᴜʏᴀ</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴇᴠᴇʀʏᴛʜɪɴɢ ᴘʀɪᴏʀ ᴛᴏ ꜰɪʀꜱᴛ ɢʀᴇᴇᴛɪɴɢ ɪꜱ ᴜᴘ ᴛᴏ ʟʟᴍ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀᴄᴋɴᴏᴡʟᴇᴅɢᴇ ʏᴏᴜʀ ᴛʀɪʙᴀʟ ᴄʜᴇꜰ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 112px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/67311507-a983-44e8-89c4-a6959d459395_19a9bfec-0999-4e82-9b2e-e6d0fac982de.webp?width=1000\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"67311507-a983-44e8-89c4-a6959d459395_7ea5c471-29cb-4a04-b771-88ec4f2419f8.webp","creator":"EminemsSalsa","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","📚 Fictional","🎮 Game","👤 AnyPOV","❤️‍🩹 Fluff"],"chats":4061,"messages":45875,"created_at":"2025-02-06T05:35:22.252716+00:00"}